sh
Copy code
cd calculator
Usage
Start the PHP Built-in Server:

sh
Copy code

Using the Calculator:

Enter the first number in the "Enter first number" field.
Enter the second number in the "Enter second number (if needed)" field. This is optional for operations like square root and logarithm.
Select the desired operation from the dropdown menu.
Click the "Calculate" button.
The result will be displayed below the form.

Testing
Ensure PHP is installed on your machine.
Start the PHP server using the command provided in the Usage section.
Use the provided web form to input numbers and select operations.
Verify the results for each type of operation to ensure the calculator works correctly.